title: 20 Amp Circuit Breaker
blurb:
Durable multi-purpose circuit breakers for AC or DC circuits. Available in current ratings between 3A and 25A.
Specifications:
• Will hold 100% of rated current indefinitely at 25°C
• Will derate at higher temperatures
• Manual push to reset
• Insulation resistance > 100M ohm
• Mounting hole diameter 12mm
